unnormalised: Konnem tor mhaka vicharlem Bharoti lok sadharan kitlo denge dhaantat mhunn. Tem ek kotthin prashnha, ani dhaanachi rashi aadain, dharmik manyata, ani vyaktigat mulyancher aadharit bhinn bhinn asta. Ekuch ani nischit jabab naslo tori, hanv thoddi mahiti divunk xakta.

Sadharan, tumhi lhan rashi Rs. 100 thavn ₹5000 vo adhik meren denge dekhunk paavtat, khas korun Diwali sarkhea festak zanna bhov lok devsthanank denge ditat vo gorjevontank bheekh ditat. Bhovdenge dhaan aupcharik ritin ghadata - tumchea buildinga bhair asa to bhikari ekeka disak bhinn bhinn lokan thavn Rs. 20 melounk xakta.

Adhik aupcharik denge dekhun, abhyasa dakhaitat ki Bharataant ekeka vorosacho sadharan dhaan ekeka monxan aaplea aadainchea 1-3% aastelem. Heo ankde sadharan sanktachya vellar chadtat. Udaharanak, COVID-19 mahamari vellar, denge chadle, ani bhov monxan ani sansthan miliona ditat, kedna-kedna $1 million vo odhik rahat divun lokank modot kortale. Bhovtenkan PM CARES fundak denge dile.

Denge dainyavishi adhik zagruti asa mhunn sangunk zai. Online platforman zanna, bhov lok lagich ani sompeponan denge divunk xaktat. Tumhi lokak UPI thavn Rs 500 casual denge ditat dekhunk xakta. Thode NGO recurring monthanchi denge ditat, ekuch udharon ₹250. Ekaeka rupia melounk ani modot korunk xakta!
